{
  "stem": "1413.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him that I was mourning for a year, and I wanted to play soccer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, since it is a physical thing, he let me play soccer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe so, because I learned in school that you have to mourn and be sitting-- all of my family was sitting Shiva for seven days.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And but I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think my father also mourned, really mourned for a year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother died in 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister-- my aunt, my father's sister, was living with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother had a rheumatic arm, and she couldn't do the chores for the house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my aunt did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she kept doing that, naturally, till [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] she went to the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But maybe I go a little further than you ask me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I'm going to come on back later onto how my aunt died, what I said a second ago, also.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was--I listen to what happened in Poland, and all those countries where anti-Semitism was very-- really minuscule.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a way of life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived between the Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you didn't live where I lived in Amsterdam, there is no comparison.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can't visualize what it is to live in Amsterdam between Jews and Gentiles because you got bad ones, you got good ones.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jewish, you got bad one and good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every nationality, I don't care how prejudiced you are, you have to admit that there are always bad ones and good people in every religion, in every race, in every color.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And nobody can deny that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, really it was just a way of life, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they give you a nickname, that was one ear in and one ear out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
